targets.rawSql:
SELECT to_timestamp(a.obj->>'timestamp', 'YYYY-MM-DD"T"HH24:MI:SS+0000') as time, to_number(a.obj->>'value', 'FM9G999D99S') as hr
FROM connector_sleepraw
CROSS JOIN LATERAL jsonb_array_elements(to_jsonb(hr_series)) AS a(obj)
WHERE start_date > $__timeFrom() AND end_date <= $__timeTo() AND (device_type = 'SLEEP_MONITOR' OR device_type = 'Aura Sensor V2')
ORDER BY time

SELECT start_date as time, CASE
  WHEN sleep_phase_id = 0 THEN 3
  WHEN sleep_phase_id = 1 THEN 1
  WHEN sleep_phase_id = 2 THEN 0
  WHEN sleep_phase_id = 3 THEN 2
END AS sleep_phase
FROM connector_sleepraw
WHERE start_date > $__timeFrom() AND end_date <= $__timeTo() AND (device_type = 'SLEEP_MONITOR' OR device_type = 'Aura Sensor V2')
ORDER BY start_date

SELECT to_timestamp(a.obj->>'timestamp', 'YYYY-MM-DD"T"HH24:MI:SS+0000') as time, to_number(a.obj->>'value', 'FM9G999D99S') as rr

CROSS JOIN LATERAL jsonb_array_elements(to_jsonb(rr_series)) AS a(obj)

SELECT to_timestamp(a.obj->>'timestamp', 'YYYY-MM-DD"T"HH24:MI:SS+0000') as time, to_number(a.obj->>'value', 'FM9G999D99S') as snor

SELECT
  end_date AS "time",
  sleep_score
FROM connector_sleepsummary
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(end_date)
ORDER BY 1

SELECT
  start_date AS "time",
  calories,
  meal
  -- AVG(weight) OVER (ORDER BY measured_at ASC ROWS 7 PRECEDING) AS "average_weight"
FROM connector_nutrition
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(start_date) AND meal='Breakfast'
ORDER BY 1

  $__timeFilter(start_date)
